@startuml
title ESP32 Alarm Clock - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Main" as Main
participant "Storage" as Storage
participant "Network" as Network
participant "SNTP" as SNTP
participant "Potentiometer" as Pot
participant "Alarm" as Alarm
participant "Display" as Display
participant "Sound" as Sound
participant "Button/Switch" as Input
queue "alarm_time_queue" as ATQ
queue "screen_status_queue" as SSQ
participant "Event Loop" as EventLoop
participant "NVS" as NVS
participant "SD Card" as SD

== Initialization Phase ==
Main -> Storage: Initialize storage
Storage -> SD: Mount SD card
activate SD
SD --> Storage: Success
deactivate SD
Storage -> NVS: Initialize NVS
activate NVS
NVS --> Storage: Success
deactivate NVS
Storage --> Main: Storage ready

Main -> Network: Initialize network
Network -> SD: Read config.json
activate SD
SD --> Network: WiFi credentials, NTP server
deactivate SD
Network -> Network: Connect to WiFi
Network -> EventLoop: Post WiFi connected event
Network -> SNTP: Initialize SNTP client
SNTP -> SNTP: Sync time with NTP server
SNTP --> Network: Time synchronized
Network --> Main: Network ready

Main -> Pot: Initialize potentiometers
Pot -> NVS: Read calibration data
activate NVS
NVS --> Pot: Calibration values
deactivate NVS
Pot --> Main: Potentiometers ready

Main -> Sound: Initialize sound system
Sound -> SD: List audio files in directory
activate SD
SD --> Sound: Audio file list
deactivate SD
Sound --> Main: Sound ready

Main -> Display: Initialize E-Paper display
Display --> Main: Display ready

Main -> Alarm: Initialize alarm
Alarm -> Alarm: Create alarm task
Alarm -> EventLoop: Register event handlers
Alarm --> Main: Alarm ready

== Runtime - Setting Alarm Time ==
User -> Pot: Adjust hour potentiometer
activate Pot
Pot -> Pot: Read ADC value
Pot -> Pot: Apply calibration
Pot -> ATQ: Send hour value
deactivate Pot

User -> Pot: Adjust minute potentiometer
activate Pot
Pot -> Pot: Read ADC value
Pot -> Pot: Apply calibration
Pot -> ATQ: Send minute value
deactivate Pot

Alarm -> ATQ: Receive alarm time
activate Alarm
Alarm -> Alarm: Update alarm time
Alarm -> SSQ: Send alarm status update
Alarm --> EventLoop: Post alarm time changed event
deactivate Alarm

Display -> SSQ: Receive status update
activate Display
Display -> Display: Render time and alarm
Display -> Display: Show alarm icon
Display --> User: Display updated
deactivate Display

== Runtime - Activating Alarm ==
User -> Input: Toggle alarm switch ON
Input -> Input: Interrupt triggered
Input -> Alarm: Alarm activation event
activate Alarm
Alarm -> Alarm: Set alarm active flag
Alarm -> SSQ: Send status update (alarm ON)
deactivate Alarm

Display -> SSQ: Receive status update
activate Display
Display -> Display: Update alarm icon (active)
Display --> User: Display shows alarm active
deactivate Display

== Runtime - Time Synchronization ==
loop Periodic sync
SNTP -> SNTP: Sync with NTP server
SNTP -> EventLoop: Post time updated event
EventLoop -> Alarm: Notify time update
activate Alarm
Alarm -> Alarm: Update current time
Alarm -> SSQ: Send current time
deactivate Alarm

EventLoop -> Display: Notify time update
activate Display
Display -> Display: Update time display
Display --> User: Show current time
deactivate Display
end

== Runtime - Alarm Triggers ==
Alarm -> Alarm: Check if alarm time reached
activate Alarm
alt Alarm time matches current time
    Alarm -> Sound: Trigger alarm sound
    activate Sound
    Sound -> SD: Select random audio file
    activate SD
    SD --> Sound: Audio file data
    deactivate SD
    Sound -> Sound: Play via I2S driver
    Sound --> User: Audio output
    deactivate Sound

    Alarm -> SSQ: Send ringing status
    Alarm -> Display: Update display (ringing)
    activate Display
    Display -> Display: Show alarm ringing indicator
    Display --> User: Display shows ringing
    deactivate Display
end
deactivate Alarm

== Runtime - Stopping Alarm ==
User -> Input: Press stop button
Input -> Input: Interrupt triggered
Input -> Alarm: Stop alarm event
activate Alarm
Alarm -> Sound: Stop playback
activate Sound
Sound -> Sound: Stop I2S output
Sound --> Alarm: Stopped
deactivate Sound

Alarm -> Alarm: Clear ringing state
Alarm -> SSQ: Send status update (stopped)
deactivate Alarm

Display -> SSQ: Receive status update
activate Display
Display -> Display: Clear ringing indicator
Display --> User: Display updated
deactivate Display

== Runtime - Snooze Alarm ==
User -> Input: Press snooze button
Input -> Input: Interrupt triggered
Input -> Alarm: Snooze alarm event
activate Alarm
Alarm -> Sound: Stop playback
activate Sound
Sound -> Sound: Stop I2S output
Sound --> Alarm: Stopped
deactivate Sound

Alarm -> Alarm: Set snooze timer
Alarm -> SSQ: Send status update (snoozed)
deactivate Alarm

Display -> SSQ: Receive status update
activate Display
Display -> Display: Show snooze indicator
Display --> User: Display updated
deactivate Display

== Runtime - Network Reconnection ==
alt WiFi disconnected
EventLoop -> Network: WiFi disconnected event
activate Network
Network -> Network: Attempt reconnection
Network -> Network: Reconnect to WiFi
Network -> EventLoop: Post WiFi reconnected event
Network --> Display: Update WiFi icon
deactivate Network

Display -> Display: Show WiFi connected icon
Display --> User: Display updated
end

== Runtime - Potentiometer Calibration ==
User -> Pot: Initiate calibration routine
activate Pot
Pot -> Pot: Read raw ADC values
Pot -> Pot: Calculate calibration factors
Pot -> NVS: Store calibration data
activate NVS
NVS --> Pot: Data saved
deactivate NVS
Pot --> User: Calibration complete
deactivate Pot

@enduml
